                    </h3>
                    <div class="p-work-overview__description">OneClick Code is a platform that simplifies the
                      process of obtaining roofing code reports for specific addresses. OCC
                      provide access to information on roofing codes, sales tax, manufacturer specifications,
                      permit fees, and jurisdictional
                      authority in one convenient location.
