                    <h3 class="p-work-overview--occ p-work-overview__title" id="the-challenge">The Challenge</h3>
                    <div class="p-work-overview__description"> The challenge of the redesign of the OC Code
                      project was to improve the user-friendliness of an existing platform that
                      simplifies the process of obtaining and utilizing roofing code reports for specific
                      addresses, making it easier for
                      professionals in the roofing industry to navigate compliance and regulations. The goal was
                      to create a more
                      aesthetically pleasing and usable design, accessible on both web and native devices, with
                      the aim of increasing the
                      conversion of users from the Starter plan to the Pro plan.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
