                      understand the market and the types of products we needed to focus on. I played a key role
                      in this process, working on
                      information architecture, wireframing, and UI design. After implementing the design in code,
                      we used the HotJar program
                      to research user behavior and gain insights into how they were using the product. This
                      helped us to make informed
                      decisions and improve the overall user experience.
                    </div>
