                    <div class="p-work-overview__description">The OCC project aimed to create a user-friendly
                      platform for the roofing industry. The team successfully developed a
                      design that simplifies the process of obtaining and utilizing roofing code reports, making
                      compliance and regulations
                      easier to navigate. The platform was well-received by users and achieved its goal of
                      increasing conversions from Starter
                      to Pro plans.
                      <h4>Key takeaways from this project are:</h4>
                      <ul>
                        <li>User testing doesn't end after development. Design
                          is a constant iteration of improving the experience for the end user.
                          Always find ways to collect and listen to your user's feedback.
                        </li>
                        <li>Involve engineering upfront. This helps to reduce any rework later on as an understanding
                          of the technical limitations
                          upfront will help to inform your design strategy.</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
